# 🎨 UI Enhancement Plan — "Quiet Elegance"

> **Theme:** Simple, elegant, and aesthetic — like a calm, well-organized notebook  
> **Philosophy:** Let content breathe. Every element earns its space. Color is used with intention, not decoration.

---

