## 4. Spacing & Radius

### Spacing — Add a breathing tier

```diff
 class AppSpacing {
   static const double xs = 4;
   static const double sm = 8;
   static const double md = 12;
   static const double lg = 16;
   static const double xl = 20;
   static const double xxl = 24;
   static const double xxxl = 32;
+  static const double section = 28;  // Between major sections
+  static const double page = 20;     // Page horizontal padding
 }
```

### Radius — Slightly rounder

```diff
 class AppRadius {
-  static const double sm = 10;
-  static const double md = 12;
-  static const double lg = 16;
-  static const double xl = 20;
+  static const double sm = 12;
+  static const double md = 14;
+  static const double lg = 18;
+  static const double xl = 22;
+  static const double pill = 999;  // Named constant for pill shapes
 }
```

> [!TIP]
> Slightly rounder corners give a softer, more modern feel — the difference between "functional" and "crafted."

