## 5. Shadow System

Replace scattered `BoxShadow` definitions with a unified elevation system:

```dart
class AppShadow {
  /// Cards resting on the surface (default state)
  static const List<BoxShadow> card = [
    BoxShadow(
      color: Color(0x08111827),
      blurRadius: 8,
      offset: Offset(0, 2),
    ),
  ];

  /// Cards on hover/pressed or elevated panels
  static const List<BoxShadow> cardElevated = [
    BoxShadow(
      color: Color(0x0C111827),
      blurRadius: 16,
      offset: Offset(0, 4),
    ),
  ];

  /// Hero/gradient cards — colored shadow
  static List<BoxShadow> hero(Color baseColor) => [
    BoxShadow(
      color: baseColor.withOpacity(0.18),
      blurRadius: 24,
      offset: const Offset(0, 10),
    ),
  ];

  /// Bottom sheets & modals
  static const List<BoxShadow> sheet = [
    BoxShadow(
      color: Color(0x14111827),
      blurRadius: 32,
      offset: Offset(0, -8),
    ),
  ];
}
```

