## 7. Shared Component Library

Create a set of reusable "elegant" primitives in `lib/widgets/`:

### 7.1 `elegant_card.dart`
```dart
/// A white card with soft shadow, consistent padding, and optional left accent.
class ElegantCard extends StatelessWidget {
  final Widget child;
  final Color? accentColor;    // Left border accent
  final EdgeInsets? padding;
  final VoidCallback? onTap;

  // Uses AppShadow.card, white bg, AppRadius.lg
}
```

### 7.2 `section_header.dart`
```dart
/// A section title with optional trailing count badge.
class SectionHeader extends StatelessWidget {
