## 8. Animation Plan

| Animation | Where | Duration | Curve |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Page content stagger** | All screens | 40ms delay per item | `easeOutCubic` |
| **Card fade-in** | Dashboard, Schedule, Notifications | 260ms | `easeOutCubic` |
| **Status pill scale-in** | Dashboard schedule cards | 180ms | `easeOutBack` |
| **Bottom nav dot** | Selected tab indicator | 200ms | `easeInOutCubic` |
| **Badge bounce** | Notification count change | 300ms | `elasticOut` |
| **Pull-to-refresh** | All data screens | System default | System default |
| **Sheet backdrop** | Notification detail | 260ms | `easeOut` |
| **Hero banner parallax** | Dashboard scroll | Continuous | Linear |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> All animations should respect `MediaQuery.disableAnimations`. The app already does this in the loading screen — extend to all new animations.

